    Summarise a View object

    summary.View.Rd

    Summarise a View object

    Usage

    # S3 method for View
summary(object, ...)

    Arguments

    object

    View object.

    ...

    ignored.

    Value

    summary of data.frame.

    Examples

    r <- get_sample_recording()
rv <- get_raw_view(r, "Central", "", "Sitar")
pv <- get_processed_view(rv)
fv <- apply_filter_sgolay(pv, c("Nose", "RWrist", "LWrist"), n=19, p=4)
summary(rv)
